Package: jpipe
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, default-jre, graphviz
Description: Justified Pipeline compiler
 jPipe is a compiler and language environment for defining justifications
 that support software maintenance and CI/CD activities.
 .
 The name comes from "justified pipelines": the key idea is to design an
 environment supporting the justification of CI/CD pipelines by design.
